# SerializationError.packageNotFound(_:)

**Case**

An error that indicates that the package at specified URL was not found.

## Declaration

```swift
case packageNotFound(URL)
```

## Analyzing the error

- **SerializationError.notRepresentableAsCoreML(debugDescription:)**: An error that indicates that the transformer cannot be represented as a CoreML model.
- **SerializationError.packageAlreadyExists(_:)**: An error that indicates that the package already exists at the URL.
